						<summary>

						<p>Stone erected in a field to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Virōdhikṛit, Mārgaśira ba. 5.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. States that Koṇḍa Nāraśiṁharāju made some repairs to the tank called Siddhirāju-Cheruvu, for his own merit, with the consent of <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Kōṭipi [Raṅga]rājayya.</p>						

